</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Click on the plus sign next to "Torso". {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ca/Make-a-VIP-T-Shirt-Door-on-Roblox-Step-6Bullet5.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-VIP-T-Shirt-Door-on-Roblox-Step-6Bullet5.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ca/Make-a-VIP-T-Shirt-Door-on-Roblox-Step-6Bullet5.jpg/v4-760px-Make-a-VIP-T-Shirt-Door-on-Roblox-Step-6Bullet5.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
