</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Go to View again, then to Properties, which will pop up under the explorer. The shirt graphic should still be highlighted. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4d/Make-a-VIP-T-Shirt-Door-on-Roblox-Step-6Bullet7.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-VIP-T-Shirt-Door-on-Roblox-Step-6Bullet7.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4d/Make-a-VIP-T-Shirt-Door-on-Roblox-Step-6Bullet7.jpg/v4-760px-Make-a-VIP-T-Shirt-Door-on-Roblox-Step-6Bullet7.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
